187
00:07:45.299 --> 00:07:46.633
♪ What if I loved you...

188
00:07:46.717 --> 00:07:48.969
Oh. my gosh. yes. This is perfection.

189
00:07:49.052 --> 00:07:50.721
So. are you coming in or what?

190
00:07:56.977 --> 00:07:59.104
