just kill me ♪

191
00:07:59.188 --> 00:08:00.522
♪ By now ♪

192
00:08:00.606 --> 00:08:04.234
♪ I should be okay ♪

193
00:08:04.318 --> 00:08:06.695
♪ What if I love? ♪♪

194
00:08:10.449 --> 00:08:12.951
There's something I need to tell you.

195
00:08:13.952 --> 00:08:14.953
Okay.

196
00:08:16.330 --> 00:08:18.624
