210
00:08:49.279 --> 00:08:51.240
Yeah. I wouldn't go that far.

211
00:08:53.200 --> 00:08:55.452
But there's something about it.

212
00:08:55.535 --> 00:08:58.497
It's like... I was in so much pain

213
00:08:58.580 --> 00:09:00.916
