♪ ships in the night ♪

884
00:42:27.671 --> 00:42:29.923
♪ one in a million ♪

885
00:42:30.006 --> 00:42:32.592
♪ stars in the sky ♪

886
00:42:33.593 --> 00:42:35.553
♪ You and I ♪

887
00:42:35.637 --> 00:42:39.057
